title: War of the Roses: Who's Dog Is Barking in the Background
description: Janelle's boyfriend, Doug will claim that he's stuck in traffic and be late for things but she's noticed that there hasn't been traffic according to some Googling so what is taking him so long to get somewhere?  And why is there a yippy dog in the background when we talk to Doug?
